    "description": "<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391710/extras/5e94af8ae590f18a9654307675abd199.poster.avif?t=1715342990\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391710/extras/5e94af8ae590f18a9654307675abd199.webm?t=1715342990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391710/extras/5e94af8ae590f18a9654307675abd199.mp4?t=1715342990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>准备踏上恢弘的正途，寻遍三颗星球十二道难关，寻回失窃的寰宇之心。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4个角色可以选择，各有各的不同，可以随心改变游戏风格，发挥自己的游戏特长。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>角色的技能组合各不相同，共有45种升级方向，助你披荆斩棘，一路向前。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>不过，千万注意安全！你将面对27种敌人的猛烈抵抗，每种敌人都有自己特有的能力和武器，给你造成不一样的难题。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>合作模式可以与朋友携手，共同对抗机器敌人。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391710/extras/e0aec2912639fe5bf8b1ced564247828.poster.avif?t=1715342990\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391710/extras/e0aec2912639fe5bf8b1ced564247828.webm?t=1715342990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391710/extras/e0aec2912639fe5bf8b1ced564247828.mp4?t=1715342990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>走进战场，找回寰宇之心，成为最终的护门者！",
